text: Ernest Parker (14 November 1895 - 28 November 1965) was a British swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke event at the 1920 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1895 births Category:1965 deaths Category:British male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Great Britain Category:Swimmers at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Sheffield Category:Male breaststroke swimmers
